      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this solid and dependable ride! It's in fair condition, showing some honest character and wear from its journeys, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a functional vehicle at a great price. With a little bit of TLC, this car has plenty of life left and is ready to be your next reliable companion!",
