    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all electronic features are fully functional. It is a reliable, attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner with no immediate service needs.",
