    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this masterfully preserved vehicle, currently offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This specimen retains its factory-original luster and mechanical precision, having undergone a comprehensive evaluation to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of excellence. For the discerning individual seeking an investment-grade automotive acquisition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to secure a benchmark example of the marque.",
      "price": 44500.0,
