    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve honestly treated it better than my own living room! It\u2019s super clean, looks stunning, and drives exactly like it did on day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically pristine, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a fully serviced VANOS system to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip variable M differential that provides exceptional lateral grip. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the vehicle exhibits no aesthetic or mechanical compromises. All fluid services are current, utilizing only OE-spec lubricants.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
